    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless condition\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've taken such good care of it, and it really shows. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, you've gotta come see this beauty. It\u2019s super clean inside and out, and I promise you won't be disappointed. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional 2002 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant. This unit is mechanically superlative, boasting a 6-speed manual Getrag transmission and a fully documented service history. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed: the rod bearings have been replaced with VAC coated bearings, and the double-VANOS system has been rebuilt with Beisan components. The rear subframe, a known weak point, has been professionally reinforced with structural plates to ensure chassis rigidity. The engine retains perfect compression across all six cylinders, breathing through factory individual throttle bodies. The exterior retains its original factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or clear coat failure. This is a turn-key, collector-grade example for the purist who values mechanical integrity and precision engineering.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
